<!--- 
Remember to change the percentage where the variables are. They'll be under :root {, just look for /* SKILLS PERCENTAGE */ and change it there.

Here's an example of what you should do if you want to add more skills:
01.) Add --skill-four:%; under :root { where /* SKILLS PERCENTAGE */ is. 
02.) Then add .bar.four { width:var(--skill-four); } under .bar.three { width:var(--skill-three); }
03.) Then come back here and add
        <p><h3>SKill #4</h3>
        <div class="hp"><div class="bar four"></div></div></p> 
04.) And that's it.
--->

